name: Wake Up
description: All proceeds of this piece will go towards a fund dedicated to encouraging talented new Bruneian cryptoartists. This interactive piece generates a triangle or a square on a 10x10 grid in a set color scheme reminiscent of the Brunei flag. Clicking anywhere triggers a new randomized generation and each run creates an opportunity to introduce a rare red-colored element! (Be careful if you're trying to right-click save as, that'll also trigger a regeneration). | Date: 12 May 21 | Artist: @Yazid
